data.description: Professionally Staged! Welcome home to this SPACIOUS RANCH with over 1800 SQFT, 3 Bedrooms PLUS 2 FULL Baths!  Also, enjoy the huge ready-to-finish lower-level w/bath rough-in! Open modern floor plan that consists of an oversize great room w/soaring cathedral ceilings, fireplace, both rooms w/luxury Vinyl Planking, a well-appointed gourmet kitchen loaded with tons of 42'' white cabinets, granite stainless appliances, breakfast bar/ breakfast dinette w/window seat also w/loads of windows! 1st Floor Laundry, Luxurious Primary Suite w/Grand Bath. Home is situated on a magnificent, private lot with extensive landscaping, a large paver patio & gazebo! Tons of upgrades & extras: Closets by Design, Designer Blinds, Deduct Meter, Gas Stove, Trendy Light Fixtures, Fenced Yard & More!!
